==Finnish==
===Noun===

''(vulgar)'' vitutus
#The status of being deeply annoyed, as described in [[vituttaa]]. Some females may like to use the word ''[[kyrvitys]]'' instead.
*A person experiencing ''vitutus'' is ''[[vittuuntunut]]''.

*Derived from [[vittu]].

*Some females may like to use the word ''[[kyrvitys]]'' instead.

*Often replaced in common language by ''hatutus'' which rhymes with vitutus, and is derived from [[hattu]].

